SENTENCE well ,  we can know for sure because in this oak forest ,  the researchers decided to test the links between acorns and the two animal species .
SENTENCE in some parts of the forest ,  they had volunteers drop a large number of extra acorns on the forest floor .
SENTENCE and in another section of the forest ,  they removed a number of white footed mice .
SENTENCE in the forest areas where extra acorns had been dropped ,  the gypsy moth population soon went into a significant decline .
SENTENCE but in the section of the forest where the white footed mice had been removed ,  the gypsy moth population exploded .
